Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:32.05,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\bord0\shad0\c&H1AB422&\fs45\pos(1320,461.25)}Nežeň sa znova!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:32.05,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\bord0\shad0\c&H1AB422&\fs45\pos(1350,153)}Kúpi mi čokoľvek chcem.
