Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:32.05,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\bord0\shad0\c&H1AB422&\fs45\pos(669,913.5)}Chcel by som aby si mi odpustil...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:32.05,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\bord0\shad0\c&H1AB422&\fs45\pos(1311,801)}Ty nám neveríš?
