Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:32.05,flying_object,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\bord0\shad0\c&H1AB422&\fs45\pos(1440,310.5)}Nie je to taký lakomec ako ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:27.31,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,A tak mi ostal len ten sentimentálny pocit.
